# RFC-0022: Wave Rendering Standard

**Subtitle:** Formal Specification for Symbolic Output  
**Status:** Standard  
**Author:** PantheonOS Tooling Division  

---

## 1. Abstract

This RFC establishes the standard for how Wave Language sentences must be processed and displayed to ensure cross-system consistency.

---

## 2. Input Specification

The Renderer MUST accept inputs in the following format:

```text
[Actor] + [Force] + [Transformation] + [State]
